to give you this back.

12:03.542 --> 12:05.670
Oh, no.
It's okay, keep it.

12:05.772 --> 12:06.737
- But...
- Keep it.

12:06.839 --> 12:08.245
And buy
a helmet.

12:08.347 --> 12:09.605
And some Kevlar, okay,

12:09.707 --> 12:11.776
if you're planning
on attending
more stuff like that.

12:11.878 --> 12:13.280
I am, yeah, going to.

12:13.382 --> 12:16.820
I'm a photographer
and I wanna be
a war photographer actually.

12:18.252 --> 12:21.355
By the way, you have
the same name as my hero.

12:21.457 --> 12:22.724
Lee Miller.

12:22.826 --> 12:24.622
