that you're also
one of my heroes.

12:35.299 --> 12:38.842
And you've got
the same name too.

12:39.473 --> 12:40.477
Wow.

12:40.579 --> 12:42.780
Thank you.
I'm in good company.

12:44.978 --> 12:47.312
- What's your name?
- Jessie.

12:47.879 --> 12:49.183
Jessie Collin.

12:49.285 --> 12:53.252
So, Jessie,
I've gotta walk up
ten flights of stairs.

12:54.658 --> 12:56.925
