27:35.101 --> 27:36.970
pretending like none of this
is happening.

27:53.650 --> 27:55.289
Lee,

27:55.959 --> 27:59.495
I'm sorry for jamming my way
into your ride, okay?

27:59.597 --> 28:01.058
